            Zero agency retainer. Zero design team. Just n8n workflows, Claude AI creative skills,
            and a production pipeline that runs while you sleep.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[13px] text-white/35 leading-relaxed">
            This is what we build for clients. Brief in. Campaign out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

