            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-[9px] text-white/20 tracking-wide uppercase">
          Produced entirely in-house using the Purist Ads Automation System · No agency · No retainer · Just workflows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
